#: ../../reference_manual/tools/freehand_brush.rst:-1:
msgid "Krita's freehand brush tool reference, containing how to use the stabilizer in krita."
msgstr "Krita での手振れ補正の使い方を含む、Krita フリーハンドブラシツールの説明。"

